1
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,560
If you get a repair now,

2
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:57,480
we can offer a free vehicle inspection.

3
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,200
All repairs are currently 50% off,

4
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,080
along with maintenance for some parts.

5
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,680
The entire car's paint job

6
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,800
and the interior are all in good condition.

7
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:03,440
Right.

8
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,319
They are quite nice.

9
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,239
You can take a look.

10
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,440
These two packages at the back

11
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:06,720
are also very suitable for you.

12
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,160
Who is in charge here?

13
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:13,000
I am. What's wrong?

14
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,560
Hello, I'm from Lucheng Daily.

15
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,200
Are you aware of

16
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,039
the assault incident at your garage?

17
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:18,320
I am a reporter from Lucheng TV.

18
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,880
Can you explain the violent assault

19
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:20,800
at your auto repair shop?

20
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,000
We received evidence that

21
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,360
someone had their car repaired here,

22
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,840
went back and found their wallet missing,

23
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,680
and when they returned to look for it,

24
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,000
they were beaten up by you guys for no reason.

25
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,440
We also received audio evidence.

26
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,520
Can you explain it?

27
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,120
Is this all nonsense?

28
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:33,960
Gao Chenyang.

29
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,039
Gao Chenyang.

30
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:35,560
This...

31
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,440
I won't deny what I did,

32
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,759
but if I didn't do it,

33
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,200
don't even think about framing us.

34
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,280
How dare he twist the truth!

35
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,240
This is too much!

36
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,200
We should have called the police earlier.

37
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,320
Excuse me, please stop filming.

38
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,039
Reporters,

39
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,400
the truth is really not like this.

40
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,800
Do you know Ding Shiyu in the recording?

41
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,840
What is your relationship? Do you know each other?

42
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,440
I'm warning you one last time, stop filming!

43
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,920
Did you really beat up a customer?

44
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,160
You have to explain this clearly.

45
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,360
Who is in charge here?

46
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:58,720
I am.

47
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,320
Hello.

48
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,960
I'm a law enforcement officer from the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

49
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:02,920
My name is Chen Bin.

50
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,720
Here is my ID.

51
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,600
We received an anonymous complaint

52
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,640
saying that your shop

53
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,080
secretly replaces customers' parts.

54
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,280
We hope you can cooperate with us.

55
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,880
This did happen before,

56
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:13,200
but we have already negotiated and settled it with the customer.

57
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,440
The compensation we offered

58
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,770
was agreed upon by them.

59
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,520
So I think

60
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,720
this must be a malicious report.

61
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,440
Regardless of the reporter's motives,

62
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:20,840
we

63
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,800
must investigate all reports.

64
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,600
Now, we hope you will cooperate

65
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,079
and suspend the shop's business activities.

66
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,680
We will conduct a comprehensive inspection.

67
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,520
During this period,

68
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,920
we will also put a notice and seal

69
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:32,640
of suspension for rectification on your shop door.

70
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,240
Of course,

71
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,960
if you have any questions,

72
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,360
you can also appeal to us.

73
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,360
Okay.

74
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,160
We will fully cooperate,

75
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,440
and hope to find out the truth as soon as possible.

76
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:44,640
Okay.

77
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,640
Did you record all of it?

78
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,640
They also secretly replaced parts.

79
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,610
Stop recording.

80
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,480
Say a few words.

81
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,320
Say a few words. I said stop recording!

82
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:52,640
Go.

83
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,200
Could you please explain?

84
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,060
Everybody out.

85
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,960
Go. Didn't you hear me talking to you?

86
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,760
Is this how you violently treat your customers?

87
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,000
Go. Don't stay here.

88
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,480
Say a few words.

89
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,400
Out.

90
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,720
We are really not like this.

91
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,240
Really.

92
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,920
The real situation is not like this.

93
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,050
Everyone, don't go.

94
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:06,720
Listen to our explanation.

95
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,380
Our factory wouldn't do this.

96
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,760
Don't go.

97
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,730
Listen to our explanation.

98
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:38,320
I don't even dare to go there for car repairs anymore.

99
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,180
Yeah, the credibility is too low.

100
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,700
I wouldn't dare to risk it.

101
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,040
I'm going to ask for my money back.

102
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,840
Who's with me?

103
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,480
Bro, it's not a big deal.

104
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,220
It's just some photos posted online.

105
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,090
If you ask me,

106
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,940
what we don't see won't bother us.

107
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,160
Just turn off your phone.

108
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,240
Exactly.

109
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,960
It's just being framed for intentional assault

110
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,360
and attacked by netizens.

111
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,240
It's not a big problem.

112
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,040
I'm telling you,

113
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,040
it's mainly because I wasn't there.

114
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:15,200
Otherwise, I would have beaten them up.

115
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,600
Yeah, beat them up.

116
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,850
The mung bean soup is ready.

117
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:28,400
Brother, it's okay.

118
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,960
We are all here. We can get through this.

119
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,840
Yeah.

120
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,000
We will always find the exit.

121
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,360
Brother Tianyu,

122
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,280
the maze is too big. I want to go out.

123
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,280
I don't want to play here anymore.

124
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,720
Don't give up.

125
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,000
We will definitely find the exit.

126
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:56,120
If I get lost in the future,

127
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,659
will you be able to find me?

128
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,460
Of course. I definitely will.

129
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,520
I always will.

130
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:03,680
Thank you.

131
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,040
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

132
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,640
Are you okay?

133
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,570
I didn't mean it.

134
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,780
Let me do it. Let me.

135
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:30,280
No wonder you're wearing long sleeves on such a hot day.

136
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:32,080
Is it because I made you bump into something just now

137
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,800
that you're trying to frame me?

138
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,880
I really didn't mean it.

139
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,800
It's fine. It's fine. I'm sorry.

140
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,800
My buddy runs a beauty salon.

141
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,930
I'll ask him for you.

142
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,200
Stay out of our family's business.

143
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,000
Come on, guys.

144
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,690
Your whole family is crazy.

145
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,280
Exactly.

146
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,960
Who would care if we weren't friends?

147
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,420
What's with the attitude?

148
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,320
Let's go. I'll help you up.

149
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:53,960
I'm sorry.

150
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,320
What a jerk.

151
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,480
What's going on with the injury on your arm?

152
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,280
Brother, what are you doing?

153
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:20,000
How long are you going to keep this from me?

154
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,960
There's only one year left until graduation.

155
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,240
It will be fine once we get through it.

156
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,570
Telling you would just add to the trouble.

157
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,480
If it wasn't for Su Wan today...

158
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,560
If it wasn't for her, I wouldn't have made a fool of myself in public.

159
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,320
But they...

160
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,200
Brother.

161
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,700
I never want to see them again.

162
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,440
I got it.

163
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,340
Get a good rest.

164
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,980
Focus on your studies.

165
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,040
I'll head out first.

166
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,570
Brother.

167
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,240
You'll always protect me, right?

168
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,740
Get a good rest.

169
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,780
Brother, here's the watermelon.

170
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,450
Are you okay?

171
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,200
I'm fine.

172
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,760
Being as clumsy as I am,

173
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,640
what will I do in the future?

174
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,610
You have me here, don't you?

175
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,280
Brother, I'm just kidding.

176
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:50,140
How can you vent your anger like this?

177
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,280
Food is innocent, sis.

178
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,000
Yuding,

179
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,800
why are you also lecturing me?

180
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,659
What are you muttering about?

181
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,160
Nothing.

182
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,360
By the way, how is Bai Qing doing?

183
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,440
I just called.

184
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,130
She said she's fine.

185
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,560
Her brother is there taking care of her,

186
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,000
so she must be in good hands.

187
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,120
Don't worry.

188
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,640
No, Su Wan.

189
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,600
Are you jealous of Bai Qing?

190
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:28,000
What if I am?

191
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,130
They are biological siblings.

192
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,720
If Bai Qing were Bai Tianyu's god-sister,

193
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,400
wouldn't you tear her apart?

194
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,559
No, I was just...

195
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,640
Yes, you are.

196
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,720
Bai Qing is really good to you.

197
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,880
Since she got hurt,

198
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,880
she hasn't said a bad word about you.

199
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,570
Your sister-in-law is really nice to you.

200
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,040
Is she?

201
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,480
Su Wan, where are you going?
